0and%20one%20that%20comes%20just%20weeks%20before%20the%20country%20is%20due%20to%20host%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20all%20expectations%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbubble-bursts-for-frances-far-right-as-voters-bar-it-from-power-6056301%5C%22%3Efar-right%20National%20Rally%20(RN)%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20pushed%20from%20a%20clear%20first%20place%20in%20the%20first%20round%20a%20week%20ago%20to%20third%20place%20in%20the%20final%20and%20second%20round%20on%20Sunday%2C%20by%20the%20New%20Popular%20Front%20(NFT)%2C%20a%20coalition%20of%20Socialists%2C%20Greens%2C%20and%20Communists.%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron's%20centrist%20alliance%20came%20second.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20voting%20and%20calls%20from%20all%20the%20other%20parties%20to%20block%20the%20far-right's%20ascent%20worked%20very%20effectively.%20In%20the%20first%20round%20a%20week%20ago%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrance-legislative-elections-disaster-averted-emmanuel-macron-still-faces-big-challenge-ahead-6056303%5C%22%3EMarine%20Le%20Pen's%20RN%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20first%20with%2030%25%20of%20the%20vote%2C%20sending%20shock%20waves%20throughout%20France%20and%20beyond.%20That%20prompted%20the%20RN's%20political%20opponents%20to%20join%20hands%20to%20defeat%20the%20far-right%20party.%20More%20than%20200%20candidates%20withdrew%20to%20allow%20a%20one-to-one%20fight%20against%20the%20party%20in%20the%20second%20and%20decisive%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20this%20pact%20has%20ensured%20that%20Le%20Pen's%20protege%2C%20the%2028-year-old%20Jordan%20Bardella%2C%20will%20now%20not%20be%20the%20next%20French%20Prime%20Minister.%20Had%20the%20results%20of%20the%20first%20round%20repeated%20through%20the%20second%2C%20Bardella%20would%20not%20only%20have%20become%20the%20youngest%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20France%20but%20also%20the%20first%20far-right%20leader%20of%20the%20country%20since%20its%20occupation%20by%20Nazi%20Germany%20under%20Adolf%20Hitler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENightmare%20for%20Macron%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20have%20thrown%20France%20into%20unchartered%20territory.%20The%20RN%20may%20have%20been%20pushed%20into%20the%20third%20place%2C%20but%20no%20group%20has%20a%20majority%20and%20no%20clear%20figure%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20possible%20future%20Prime%20Minister.%20This%20is%20a%20nightmare%20for%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20and%20his%20country%2C%20which%20is%20a%20major%20global%20power%2C%20a%20member%20of%20NATO%2C%20and%20a%20permanent%20member%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%20Macron%20had%20called%20the%20snap%20elections%20a%20month%20ago%20to%20seek%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bclarification%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20far-right%20gave%20his%20alliance%20a%20painful%20drubbing%20in%20the%20European%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20decision%20was%20criticised%20a%20lot%20because%20it%20was%20a%20huge%20gamble.%20Bardella%2C%20though%2C%20was%20delighted%2C%20because%20it%20was%20he%20who%20demanded%20fresh%20elections.%20Macron's%20gamble%20had%20ultimately%20failed%20as%20it%20brought%20the%20NR%20closer%20to%20power%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Unnatural%20Alliance'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20final%20round%20now%2C%20Bardella%20has%20criticised%20the%20%26quot%3Bunnatural%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdishonourable%20alliance%26quot%3B%20that%20has%20%26quot%3Bdeprived%20the%20French%20people%26quot%3B%20of%20an%20RN%20victory.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20months%20now%2C%20a%20wind%20of%20hope%20has%20picked%20up%20and%20it%20will%20never%20stop%20blowing%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-elections-france-elections-tale-of-two-elections-how-voters-in-uk-france-turned-on-their-leaders-6039613%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0Tale%20Of%20Two%20Elections%3A%20How%20Voters%20In%20UK%2C%20France%20Turned%20On%20Their%20Leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron's%20problems%20have%20just%20begun.%20He%20will%20now%20have%20to%20live%20with%20what%20is%20known%20in%20France%20as%20'cohabitation'.%20The%20President%20is%20the%20head%20of%20state%2C%20but%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20accountable%20to%20Parliament%2C%20leads%20the%20government%2C%20and%20introduces%20bills.%20According%20to%20the%20French%20constitution%2C%20the%20President%20is%20the%20commander-in-chief%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20but%20the%20Constitution%20also%20says%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20responsible%20for%20national%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUncertainty%20Looms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron's%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Gabriel%20Attal%2C%20has%20already%20announced%20his%20resignation.%20There%20will%20be%20a%20period%20of%20haggling%20over%20building%20a%20coalition%20around%20a%20common%20minimum%20programme.%20This%20could%20take%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20has%20said%20he%20would%20not%20work%20with%20the%20hard-left%20France%20Unbowed%20party%2C%20but%20he%20could%20offer%20a%20hand%20to%20the%20Socialists%20and%20the%20Greens.%20However%2C%20they%20may%20not%20agree%20with%20him.%20Even%20after%20the%20parties%20decide%20on%20the%20next%20government%2C%20Macron%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20appoint%20a%20Prime%20Minister%20from%20a%20party%20that%20is%20not%20from%20his%20own%20centrist%20coalition%20and%20has%20a%20different%20political%20agenda.%20That%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20confrontation%20between%20Macron%20and%20the%20new%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fus-uk-france-iran-why-are-people-done-with-their-governments-6059808%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20France%2C%20Iran%3A%20Why%20Are%20People%20Done%20With%20Their%20Governments%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20France%20has%20a%20history%20of%20cohabitation%2C%20its%20President%20has%20never%20worked%20with%20a%20hung%20Parliament%20and%20a%20minority%20government.%20The%20modern%20French%20Republic%20has%20had%20three%20cohabitations.%20The%20last%20one%20was%20under%20conservative%20President%20Jacques%20Chirac%2C%20with%20Socialist%20Prime%20Minister%20Lionel%20Jospin%2C%20from%201997%20to%202002.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20NFT%20does%20not%20have%20a%20majority%20means%20it%20will%20have%20to%20work%20with%20Macron's%20coalition%20to%20govern%20the%20country%2C%20which%20could%20make%20things%20slightly%20easier%20for%20both.%20But%20on%20policies%2C%20the%20two%20groups%20are%20too%20far%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EContentious%20Issues%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NFT%20coalition%20parties%20are%20unlikely%20to%20back%20Macron's%20stance%20on%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20and%20will%20press%20him%20to%20take%20a%20more%20critical%20line%20against%20Israel.%20They%20will%20also%20try%20to%20push%20him%20to%20overturn%20some%20of%20his%20domestic%20policies%20(such%20as%20pension%20reform)%2C%20which%20have%20been%20deeply%20unpopular%20and%20provoked%20weeks%20of%20protests%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20election%20campaign%2C%20the%20NFP%20promised%20to%20scrap%20the%20pension%20and%20immigration%20reforms%20passed%20by%20the%20outgoing%20French%20government%20and%20to%20set%20up%20a%20rescue%20agency%20for%20undocumented%20migrants.%20It%20also%20wants%20to%20put%20price%20caps%20on%20basic%20goods%20and%20raise%20the%20minimum%20wage.%20The%20French%20economy%2C%20the%20second%20biggest%20in%20the%20EU%20after%20Germany%2C%20is%20not%20in%20decent%20shape%20and%20Macron%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20accept%20some%20of%20the%20demands%20that%20he%20will%20not%20find%20fiscally%20prudent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20a%20new%20governing%20coalition%20is%20formed%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20smooth%20sailing%20for%20France.%20The%20RN%20has%20greatly%20increased%20its%20representation%20in%20the%20newly%20elected%20Parliament%2C%20which%20will%20only%20embolden%20it%20and%20prompt%20them%20to%20work%20harder%20next%20time.%20Le%20Pen%2C%20who%20has%20unsuccessfully%20contested%20French%20presidential%20elections%20three%20times%2C%20will%20fight%20the%202027%20election%20with%20greater%20enthusiasm.%20If%20the%20new%20French%20government%20does%20not%20fulfil%20people's%20expectations%2C%20she%20could%20end%20up%20becoming%20the%20President%20of%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Le%20Pen%20Strengthened%20The%20Far-Right%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarine%20Le%20Pen%20has%20been%20working%20towards%20this%20goal%20since%202012%2C%20when%20she%20took%20over%20the%20National%20Front%20from%20her%20father%2C%20Jean-Marie%20Le%20Pen.%20He%20was%20convicted%20of%20hate%20speech%20multiple%20times%20and%20was%20never%20popular%20in%20the%20country%20beyond%20a%20small%20group.%20His%20daughter%20changed%20the%20party's%20name%20to%20National%20Rally%20and%20started%20transforming%20it%20straight%20away%20to%20broaden%20its%20base.%20It%20attracted%20support%20from%20many%20unemployed%20youth%20and%20those%20who%20felt%20left%20behind%20amid%20globalisation%20and%20rising%20levels%20of%20immigration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELe%20Pen%20based%20herself%20in%20the%20northern%20French%20town%20of%20Henin-Beaumont%2C%20which%20was%20once%20a%20base%20of%20socialists%2C%20though%20they%20were%20becoming%20increasingly%20unpopular%20because%20of%20corruption%20and%20unemployment.%20She%20picked%20up%20young%20Bardella%20and%20groomed%20him%20to%20be%20her%20deputy%2C%20which%20was%20part%20of%20a%20carefully%20crafted%20strategy.%20The%20party%2C%20which%20once%20only%20attracted%20older%20people%20unhappy%20with%20the%20growing%20immigration%20from%20North%20Africa%2C%20now%20attracted%20youths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBardella%20announced%20a%20new%20programme%20that%20promised%20to%20promote%20law%20and%20order%2C%20tighten%20the%20regulation%20for%20migration%2C%20and%20restrict%20some%20social%20benefits%20like%20housing%20to%20only%20French%20citizens.%20He%20said%20that%20dual%20citizens%20would%20be%20barred%20from%20some%20key%20jobs%2C%20such%20as%20state%20employees%2C%20in%20the%20defence%20and%20security%20field.%20He%20also%20promised%20to%20cut%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrances-allies-relieved-by-le-pen-loss-but-worry-about-messy-coalition-6057887%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0France's%20Allies%20Relieved%20By%20Le%20Pen%20Loss%20But%20Worry%20About%20Messy%20Coalition%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20issues%20appealed%20to%20a%20larger%20section%20of%20the%20society%2C%20though%20they%20also%20alarmed%20many%20who%20said%20they%20conflicted%20with%20French%20values.%20That%20was%20one%20of%20the%20main%20reasons%20why%20the%20party%20found%20itself%20in%20third%20place%20after%20the%20final%20results%2C%20as%20many%20immigrants%20and%20voters%20from%20other%20European%20backgrounds%20decided%20to%20oppose%20the%20RN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resurgence%20of%20the%20far-right%20in%20France%20is%20only%20in%20line%20with%20what%20has%20been%20happening%20elsewhere%20in%20Europe.%20There%20are%20already%20six%20hard-right%20governments%20in%20Europe.%20Some%20of%20the%20European%20far-right%20parties%20have%20roots%20in%20fascism%2C%20like%20Italy's%20governing%20Brothers%20of%20Italy%20party.%20The%20country's%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Giorgia%20Meloni%2C%20once%20used%20to%20praise%20fascist%20dictator%20Benito%20Mussolini.%20But%20for%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20she%20worked%20to%20broaden%20her%20appeal%2C%20like%20Le%20Pen%20in%20France.%20Meloni%20remains%20careful%20not%20to%20spoil%20the%20reformed%20image.%20Last%20week%2C%20she%20censured%20her%20party's%20youth%20wing%20when%20some%20of%20its%20members%20were%20captured%20on%20video%20giving%20fascist%20salutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20The%20Results%20Affect%20India%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20change%20in%20France%20is%20unlikely%20to%20make%20much%20difference%20to%20its%20India%20policy%2C%20except%20in%20terms%20of%20some%20potential%20critical%20statements%20by%20leftist%20members%20in%20the%20new%20government%20about%20India's%20human%20rights%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance%20has%20emerged%20as%20India's%20strongest%20Western%20friend%20in%20recent%20years.%20It%20is%20now%20the%20second-biggest%20supplier%20of%20arms%20to%20India%20after%20Russia.%20Last%20year%2C%20both%20countries%20celebrated%20the%2025th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Franco-Indian%20strategic%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarendra%20Modi%20and%20Macron%20have%20developed%20a%20close%20relationship%20that%20has%20helped%20both%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Paris.%20France%20even%20used%20its%20veto%20at%20the%20UN%20in%202019%20to%20block%20an%20attempt%20by%20China%20and%20Pakistan%20to%20convene%20a%20Security%20Council%20meeting%20on%20Kashmir%20after%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20by%20India.%20Macron%20has%20said%20he%20will%20not%20step%20down%20before%20the%20end%20of%20his%20term%20in%202027.%20But%20his%20remaining%20time%20in%20office%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20easy.%20He%20is%20due%20to%20attend%20a%20NATO%20summit%20this%20week%20in%20Washington%2C%20while%20his%20country%20is%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20political%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Naresh%20Kaushik%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20commentator%20based%20in%20London.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720443000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Frrvrj5a8_macron_625x300_08_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https