nt%20years%20have%20seen%20a%20transformation.%20Films%20like%20'Fire'%20and%20'Ek%20Ladki%20Ko%20Dekha%20Toh%20Aisa%20Laga'%20marked%20milestones.%20Trans%20women%20like%20Mairembam%20Ronaldo%20Singh%20in%20'Paatal%20Lok'%20and%20activists%20like%20Gazal%20Dhaliwal%20and%20Living%20Smile%20Vidya%20are%20reshaping%20narratives%2C%20promoting%20inclusivity%20and%20authentic%20representation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Milana%20Rao%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ammunition%20Vending%20Machines%20Appear%20In%20US%20Stores%20Amid%20Increasing%20Gun%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20increasing%20gun%20violence%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20some%20grocery%20stores%20around%20the%20country%20now%20have%20vending%20machines%20that%20are%20stocked%20with%20ammunition.%20A%20company%20has%20installed%20automated%20kiosks%20in%20grocery%20stores%2C%20allowing%20gun%20owners%20in%20three%20US%20states%20to%20purchase%20rounds%20from%20these%20devices%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fus%2Fnews%2F2024%2F07%2F07%2Fbullets-ammunition-vending-machines-three-american-states%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20certain%20stores%20in%20Texas%2C%20Oklahoma%2C%20and%20Alabama%2C%20people%20can%20now%20obtain%20ammunition%20for%20their%20firearms%20by%20just%20scanning%20their%20ID%20on%20a%20machine%20that%20resembles%20a%20drinks%20vending%20machine.%20The%20machines'%20manufacturer%2C%20American%20Rounds%2C%20claims%20that%20operating%20them%20is%20just%20like%20using%20an%20ATM.%20%26quot%3BOur%20automated%20ammo%20dispensers%20are%20accessible%2024%2F7%2C%20ensuring%20that%20you%20can%20buy%20ammunition%20on%20your%20own%20schedule%2C%20free%20from%20the%20constraints%20of%20store%20hours%20and%20long%20lines%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20vending%20machines%2C%20according%20to%20the%20firm%2C%20contain%20%26quot%3Bbuilt-in%20AI%20technology%2C%20card%20scanning%20capability%2C%20and%20facial%20recognition%20software.%26quot%3B%20According%20to%20American%20Rounds%2C%20the%20software%20can%20confirm%20the%20buyer's%20identity%20and%20ascertain%20if%20the%20machine%20matches%20the%20identity%20scanned.%20Customers%20use%20a%20touchscreen%20to%20pick%20the%20ammunition%20they%20want%20to%20purchase%2C%20then%20the%20machine%20scans%20their%20ID%20to%20retrieve%20it%20through%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20bottom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fammunition-vending-machines-grocery-stores-1921976%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENewsweek%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20eight%20machines%20installed%20or%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20installed%20across%20four%20states.%26quot%3B%20The%20first%20machine%20was%20installed%20at%20a%20Pell%20City%2C%20Alabama%2C%20Fresh%20Value%20grocery%20shop.%20Since%20then%2C%20four%20have%20been%20placed%20at%20Super%20C%20Marts%20in%20Oklahoma%20and%20one%20in%20Canyon%20Lake%2C%20Texas%2C%20at%20Lowe's%20Market.%20Another%20is%20being%20placed%20at%20LaGrees%20Food%20Stores%20in%20Buena%20Vista%2C%20Colorado%2C%20and%20another%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20installed%20shortly%20in%20a%20Lowes%20Market%20in%20Canyon%20Lake%2C%20said%20CEO%20of%20American%20Rounds%2C%20Grants%20Magers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20over%20200%20store%20requests%20for%20AARM%20(Automated%20Ammo%20Retail%20Machine)%20units%20covering%20approximately%20nine%20states%20currently%20and%20that%20number%20is%20growing%20daily%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Newsweek.%20Mr%20Magers%20stated%20that%20the%20company%20supported%20%26quot%3Blaw-abiding%2C%20responsible%20gun%20ownership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCurrently%20ammunition%20is%20sold%20off%20the%20shelf%20or%20online.%20These%20environments%20lead%20to%20inadvertent%20sales%20to%20underaged%20purchasers%20and%20or%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20retail%20stores%2C%20a%20high%20theft%20rate.%20What%20we%20loved%20about%20this%20concept%20is%20the%20AARM%20units%20use%20state-of-the-art%20ID%20scanners%20combined%20with%20facial%20recognition%20before%20a%20transaction%20can%20be%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20as%20per%20Oklahoma%20TV%20station%20KOCO-TV%2C%20there%20is%20no%20limitation%20on%20the%20quantity%20of%20ammunition%20customers%20can%20purchase%20and%20the%20vending%20machines%20would%20be%20restocked%20every%20two%20to%20four%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20machine%20in%20Alabama%20was%20recently%20removed%20after%20its%20legality%20was%20debated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETuscaloosa%20City%20Council%20President%20Kip%20Tyner%20said%20that%20he%20initially%20thought%20the%20machines%20were%20a%20joke%20after%20he%20received%20calls%20about%20them.%20President%20of%20the%20Tuscaloosa%20City%20Council%20Kip%20Tyner%20stated%20that%20when%20he%20first%20started%20receiving%20calls%20regarding%20the%20machines%2C%20he%20assumed%20they%20were%20a%20prank.%20%26quot%3BI%20got%20some%20calls%20about%20ammunition%20being%20sold%20in%20grocery%20stores%2C%20vending%20machines.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20lie.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20joke-but%20it's%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20machines%20are%20authorised%20by%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Alcohol%2C%20Tobacco%2C%20Firearms%20and%20Explosives%20(ATF)%20and%20are%20lawful%2C%20according%20to%20Tuscaloosa%20Police%20Chief%20Brent%20Blankley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20the%20same%2C%20Mr%20Magers%20told%20Newsweek%3A%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20Rounds%20made%20the%20business%20decision%20to%20relocate%20the%20Fresh%20Value%20Automated%20Ammo%20Retail%20Machine%20located%20in%20Tuscaloosa%20to%20another%20store%20location.%20This%20was%20strictly%20a%20business%20decision%20based%20on%20sales%20at%20that%20specific%20store.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720442100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F22rk5jbg_american-rounds_625x300_08_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fammunition-vending-machines-appear-in-us-grocery-stores-amid-increasing-gun-violence-6060713%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20no%20limitation%20on%20the%20quantity%20of%20ammunition%20customers%20can%20purchase%20and%20the%20vending%20machines%20would%20be%20restocked%20every%20two%20to%20four%20weeks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fammunition-vending-machines-appear-in-us-grocery-stores-amid-increasing-gun-violence-6060713%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fammunition-vending-machines-appear-in-us-grocery-stores-amid-increasing-gun-violence-6060713%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fammunition-vending-machines-appear-in-us-grocery-stores-amid-increasing-gun-violence-6060713%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mass%20brawl%20on%20flight%20forces%20pilot%20to%20make%20emergency%20landing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720442074000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111582017%2Cimgsize-1101162.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fmass-brawl-on-ryanair-flight-forces-pilot-to-make-emergency-landing-a-family-was-asked-to-swap-seat%2Farticleshow%2F111582051.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%8BA%20Ryanair%20flight%20last%20week%20had%20to%20be%20diverted%20when%20it%20was%20flying%20at%2030%2C000%20feet%20as%20a%20fight%20between%20two%20families%20became%20a%20mass%20brawl%20--%2030%20minutes%20into%20the%20flight.%20Footage%20published%20by