20Drinking%20At%20A%20Bar%2C%20Bill%20Emerges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMihir%20Shah%2C%20son%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Rajesh%20Shah%20and%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20the%20BMW%20hit-and-run%20in%20Mumbai%20that%20killed%20a%20woman%2C%20remains%20missing%20and%20six%20police%20teams%20are%20looking%20for%20him.%20Amid%20investigations%2C%20a%20liquor%20bill%20of%20Rs%2018%2C730%20has%20emerged%20from%20a%20bar%20in%20Juhu%20where%20the%2024-year-old%20was%20seen%20shortly%20before%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMihir%20Shah's%20father%20and%20his%20driver%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20helping%20him%20escape%20after%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20months%20after%20a%20similar%20case%20in%20Pune%2C%20in%20which%20a%20speeding%20Porsche%20driven%20by%20a%20minor%20left%20two%2024-year-old%20engineers%20dead%20in%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20investigation%20so%20far%2C%20Mihir%20Shah%20drank%20at%20a%20bar%20in%20Juhu%20till%20late%20Saturday%20night%20and%20his%20driver%20picked%20him%20up%20in%20the%20BMW%20car.%20At%20Worli%2C%20the%20politician's%20son%20allegedly%20insisted%20on%20driving%20and%20took%20over%20from%20the%20driver.%20Kaveri%20Nakhava%20and%20her%20husband%20Pradeep%20Nakhava%2C%20Koliwada%20residents%20who%20sold%20fish%20for%20a%20living%2C%20were%20on%20their%20way%20back%20from%20Sassoon%20Dock%20when%20the%20BMW%20crashed%20into%20their%20scooter.%20Kaveri%20Nakhawa%20was%20run%20over%20and%20dragged%20by%20the%20BMW%20as%20it%20fled%20the%20scene.%20She%20was%20rushed%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20where%20doctors%20declared%20her%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20under%20new%20criminal%20laws%20under%20sections%20relating%20to%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%2C%20rash%20driving%20and%20destruction%20of%20evidence%2C%20among%20others.%20The%20Motor%20Vehicles%20Act%20has%20also%20been%20invoked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vehicle%20is%20registered%20in%20Mihir%20Shah's%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20have%20said%20the%20Sena%20leader's%20son%20called%20his%20father%20and%20told%20him%20about%20the%20crash.%20His%20phone%20has%20been%20switched%20off%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim's%20husband%2C%20Pradeep%2C%20broke%20down%20before%20the%20media%20yesterday.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20two%20children%2C%20what%20will%20I%20do%20now%3F%20These%20are%20big%20people%2C%20nobody%20will%20do%20anything%2C%20we%20will%20suffer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20head%20Eknath%20Shinde%20on%20Sunday%20said%20the%20law%20was%20equal%20for%20everyone%20and%20no%20one%20would%20be%20spared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20law%20is%20equal%20for%20all%20and%20the%20government%20sees%20every%20case%20in%20the%20same%20way.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20separate%20rule%20for%20this%20accident.%20Everything%20will%20be%20done%20as%20per%20the%20law...%20The%20police%20will%20not%20shield%20anyone.%20The%20Mumbai%20accident%20is%20unfortunate.%20I%20have%20spoken%20to%20the%20police%20department%20to%20take%20strict%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720440780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fqjmmo5b4_bmw-bill-1200_625x300_08_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbmw-hit-and-run-case-mihir-shah-shiv-sena-leader-son-hours-before-bmw-crash-sena-leaders-son-was-drinking-at-a-bar-bill-emerges-6060392%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mihir%20Shah%2C%20son%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Rajesh%20Shah%20and%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20the%20BMW%20hit-and-run%20in%20Mumbai%20that%20killed%20a%20woman%2C%20remains%20missing%20and%20six%20police%20teams%20are%20looking%20for%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbmw-hit-and-run-