eet-ug%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENEET-UG%20exam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20results%20of%20which%20were%20released%20last%20month%20and%20have%20been%20marred%20by%20leaked%20questions%20and%20the%20award%20of%20'grace%20marks'%2C%20or%20preferential%20marking%2C%20for%201%2C563%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20certain%20circumstances%20-%20specifically%20%26quot%3B(if)%20the%20time%20lag%20between%20the%20leak%20and%20exam%20is%20limited%26quot%3B%20-%20would%20argue%20against%20a%20re-test.%20%26quot%3BIf%20students%20were%20asked%20to%20memorise%20(leaked%20questions)%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20exam%2C%20the%20leak%20might%20not%20have%20been%20so%20widespread...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-judge%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20it%20therefore%20was%20loathe%20to%20order%20a%20re-test%20for%20nearly%2024%20lakh%20students%20-%20many%20of%20whom%20come%20from%20poor%20families%20and%20could%20ill-afford%20to%20spend%20money%20travelling%20to%20exam%20centres%20-%20unless%20necessary.%20A%20re-test%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Blast%20option%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-updates-supreme-court-begins-hearing-on-neet-exam-irregularities-6058876%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BExam's%20Sanctity%20Compromised%26quot%3B%3A%20Court%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20is%20clear...%20questions%20were%20leaked.%20The%20sanctity%20of%20the%20exam%20has%20been%20compromised...%20this%20is%20beyond%20doubt.%20Now%20we%20have%20to%20establish%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20leak%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20be%20careful%20while%20ordering%20a%20re-test.%20We%20are%20dealing%20with%20the%20careers%20of%20lakhs%20of%20students.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20cancel%20because%20some%20students%20cheated.%20We%20must%20be%20careful...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20a%20re-test%20could%20only%20be%20ordered%20if%20there%20was%20sufficient%20time%20(the%20court%20did%20not%20specify%20how%20much%20this%20should%20be)%20between%20the%20leak%20of%20the%20questions%20and%20conduct%20of%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20or%20if%20we%20can't%20identify%20candidates%20who%20are%20guilty%20of%20wrongdoing%2C%20then%20a%20retest%20has%20to%20be%20ordered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20subject%20of%20the%20time%20lag%2C%20the%20court%20also%20sought%20details%20about%20the%20printing%20process%20and%2C%20in%20a%20humorous%20aside%2C%20reminded%20the%20NTA%20(the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%2C%20the%20central%20body%20that%20conducts%20the%20exam)%20to%20not%20reveal%20details.%20The%20NTA%20had%20been%20served%20a%20notice%20by%20the%20court%20two%20weeks%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-issues-notice-to-exam-body-nta-over-alleged-inconsistencies-in-neet-ug-marks-calculations-5980156%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECourt%20Notice%20To%20NTA%20Over%20Alleged%20%26quot%3BInconsistent%20Marks%26quot%3B%20In%20NEET%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20instead%20of%20ordering%20an%20immediate%20re-test%2C%20the%20court%20advised%20the%20constitution%20of%20a%20multi-disciplinary%20panel%20to%20probe%20this%20issue%2C%20which%20is%20already%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI's%20investigation%20spans%20multiple%20states%20and%20has%20already%20led%20to%20the%20questioning%20of%20individuals%20and%20several%20arrests%20connected%20to%20the%20case.%20The%20next%20hearing%20in%20this%20case%20has%20been%20set%20for%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20also%20rapped%20the%20government%20for%20being%20in%20%26quot%3Bdenial%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bruthless%26quot%3B%20in%20dealing%20with%20candidates%20who%20paid%20for%20the%20leaked%20exam%20and%20those%20who%20supplied%20the%20question%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20us%20not%20be%20in%20self-denial%20about%20what%20happened...%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%2C%20also%20including%20Justice%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BAssuming%20we%20do%20not%20cancel%2C%20what%20will%20the%20government%20do%20to%20identify%20the%20beneficiaries%3F%20You%20have%20to%20be%20ruthless...%20bring%20some%20sense%20of%20confidence%20to%20the%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BCancelling%20Exam%20Jeopardises%20Students'%20Future%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20the%20government%20said%20it%20does%20not%20intend%20to%20cancel%20the%20May%205%20exam%20or%20hold%20a%20re-test%2C%20and%20insisted%20there%20were%20no%20large-scale%20irregularities%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20NEET-UG%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-be-rational-to-scrap-entire-exam-centre-to-supreme-court-on-neet-6040120%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWon't%20Be%20Rational%20To%20Scrap%20Entire%20Exam%26quot%3B%3A%20Centre%20To%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubmitting%20an%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20will%20hear%20petitions%20on%20the%20issue%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20Centre%20said%20scrapping%20the%202024%20exam%20in%20its%20entirety%20would%20%26quot%3Bseriously%20jeopardise%26quot%3B%20the%20future%20lakhs%20of%20honest%20candidates%20who%20appeared%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%20the%20court%20had%20been%20told%20question%20papers%20were%20available%20on%20social%20media%2C%20including%20popular%20messaging%20apps%20like%20Telegram%2C%20at