22%3Ea%20time%20before%20smartphones.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%2C%20interacting%20with%20people%20online%20is%20as%20natural%20as%20doing%20it%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20that%20it%20has%20become%20less%20common%20for%20young%20Americans%20to%20receive%20compliments%20from%20strangers%20or%20to%20be%20asked%20out%20by%20someone%20they%20just%20met%20in%20real%20life%2C%20experts%20say%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20may%20not%20be%20a%20bad%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226bba41c6-e298-4e21-a301-a2b8efadc409%5C%22%3EThe%20fall%20of%20the%20flirt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20not%20flirting%20anymore.%20I%20hear%20this%20from%20clients%20of%20all%20ages%2C%26quot%3B%20Eimear%20Draper%2C%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkindlingdating.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKindling%20Dating%20Coaching%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDraper%2C%20who%20works%20with%20clients%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2026%20and%2073%2C%20said%20the%20rise%20of%20dating%20apps%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20pandemic%20could%20be%20to%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20long%20time%2C%20that%20'chatting%20to%20strangers'%20muscle%20wasn't%20exercised%2C%20and%20potentially%20for%20some%2C%20social%20anxiety%20has%20developed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20popularity%20of%20online%20dating%20has%20grown%20steadily%20over%20the%20past%20six%20years.%20According%20to%20the%20online%20data%20platform%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Foutlook%2Femo%2Fdating-services%2Fonline-dating%2Fworldwide%23revenue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStatista%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20online%20dating%20industry%20was%20worth%20%241.89%20billion%20in%202019%20and%20is%20predicted%20to%20grow%20to%20%243.15%20billion%20in%20global%20revenue%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDating%20apps%20are%20most%20popular%20in%20the%20US%2C%20where%20the%20industry%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fstatistics%2F1358059%2Fglobal-revenue-largest-online-dating-markets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealmost%20%241.4%20billion%20in%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Statista.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaxine%20Williams%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20single%20events%20group%20We%20Met%20IRL%2C%20told%20NBC%20that%20social%20isolation%20during%20the%20pandemic%20prevented%20young%20people%20from%20developing%20the%20skills%20required%20to%20form%20meaningful%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22gen%20z%20couple%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668bb5ef1aace5b3ada4ea9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGen%20Zers%20are%20changing%20the%20way%20they%20approach%20dating.%3Cp%3EThomas%20Barwick%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20BI%2C%20relationship%20coach%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.raileymolinario.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERailey%20Molinario%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20many%20Gen%20Zers%20feel%20%26quot%3Bmore%20comfortable%20expressing%20interest%20through%20texts%2C%20emojis%2C%20and%20social%20media%20engagement%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20%26quot%3Bdirect%2C%20personal%20encounters%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20traditional%20flirting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoung%20people%20are%20also%20less%20inclined%20to%20date%20strangers%20than%20the%20generations%20that%20came%20before%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20Survey%20Center%20on%20American%20Life%2C%20previously%20cited%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-dating-trend-online-apps-friends-romantic-partners-relationships-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20found%20that%2043%25%20of%20people%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2018%20and%2029%20were%20friends%20with%20their%20partner%20before%20they%20started%20dating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20an%20estimated%2021%25%20of%20people%20over%2065%20said%20they%20were%20friends%20with%20their%20partner%20before%20getting%20into%20a%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMolinario%20said%20the%20lack%20of%20traditional%20flirting%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20decrease%20in%20social%20skills%2C%20%26quot%3Blike%20reading%20body%20language%2C%20picking%20up%20on%20social%20cues%2C%20and%20engaging%20in%20spontaneous%20conversation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20can%20make%20it%20more%20difficult%20for%20young%20people%20to%20form%20deep%2C%20meaningful%20relationships%20in%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b61c7ec2-f0ca-4075-bdad-e6e266c5b774%5C%22%3EThe%20dating%20landscape%20has%20changed%20for%20good%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20Molinario%20said%20the%20switch%20to%20digital%20has%20benefits.%20For%20example%2C%20she%20said%20those%20expressing%20a%20romantic%20interest%20in%20someone%20online%20can%20do%20so%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20the%20immediate%20pressure%20of%20in-person%20rejection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20also%20provides%20a%20layer%20of%20safety%2C%20as%20interactions%20can%20be%20more%20easily%20controlled%20and%20monitored%20in%20digital%20spaces%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20that%20rejection%20doesn't%20exist%20online.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffancy-first-date-no-connection-ghosted-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BGhosting%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20when%20someone%20abruptly%20cuts%20off%20communication%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-deal-with-quiet-quitting-relationship-what-do-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bquiet%20quitting%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20when%20someone%20does%20the%20bare%20minimum%20without%20officially%20ending%20the%20relationship%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be%20hurtful.%20Williams%20told%20NBC%20that%20the%20internet%20has%20created%20a%20buffer%20for%20young%20people%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20rejection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20clear%20there's%20an%20appetite%20for%20the%20return%20of%20in-person%20interactions.%20Eventbrite%20reported%20that%20searches%20on%20its%20ticketing%20platform%20for%20in-person%20events%20increased%20by%201.5%20million%20over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20NBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20attendees%20at%20her%20singles%20events%20group%20told%20her%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bmore%20open%20to%20going%20into%20events%20alone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20worth%20noting%20that%20the%20fall%20of%20traditional%20flirting%20isn't%20entirely%20dependent%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20digital%20dating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbriannaparuolo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBriana%20Paruolo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20psychotherapist%20and%20founder%20of%20On%20Par%20Therapy%20NYC%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20traditional%20flirting%20has%20been%20replaced%20with%20a%20more%20direct%20and%20open%20communication%20style%20that%20she%20has%20witnessed%20both%20online%20and%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20Gen%20Z%20approaches%20flirting%20and%20relationships%20has%20certainly%20shifted%20from%20other%20generations%2C%20but%20that%20isn't%20necessarily%20a%20bad%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParuolo%20said%20she%20works%20with%20Gen%20Z%20clients%20who%20approach%20dating%20with%20self-awareness%2C%20assertiveness%2C%20open%20communication%2C%20and%20intentionality.%20She%20added%20that%20young%20people%20are%20more%20open%20and%20explicit%20about%20their%20intentions%20and%20desires%2C%20%26quot%3Beliminating%20potential%20misunderstandings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Paruolo%2C%20Gen%20Zers%20have%20a%20greater%20understanding%20of%20their%20preferences%20and%20boundaries%20when%20dating%20compared%20with%20other%20generations%2C%20which%20means%20they%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20form%20real%20emotional%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20new%20form%20of%20digital%20flirting%20that%20is%20also%20more%20suited%20to%20Gen%20Z's%20communication%20style%20and%20preferences%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20generation's%20approach%20often%20emphasizes%20an%20emotional%20connection%20and%20understanding%2C%20which%20can%20happen%20in%20real%20life%20or%20a%20digital%20landscape.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-zers-cant-flirt-could-make-dating-better-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720439698000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668bb6071aace5b3ada4ea9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-zers-cant-flirt-could-make-dating-better-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gen%20Zers%20have%20ditched%20traditional%20flirting%20methods%2C%20and%20experts%20say%20it%20could%20have%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20the%20dating%20landscape.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfriel%40businessinsider.com%20(Mikhaila%20Friel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-zers-cant-flirt-could-make-dating-better-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20NATO%20member%20said%20Ukraine%20joining%20the%20alliance%20is%20'irreversible'%20as%20fears%20mount%20that%20Trump%20would%20block%20membership%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukraine's%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskiy%20and%20Estonian%20President%20Alar%20Karis%20look%20at%20each%20other%20and%20shake%20hands%20in%20front%20of%20Estonian%2C%20EU%2C%20a