CrPC)%20of%201973%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%20of%201872%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overhaul%2C%20however%2C%20has%20sparked%20criticism%20from%20some%20lawyers%20and%20activists%20who%20argue%20that%20the%20changes%20could%20increase%20the%20power%20of%20the%20police%20over%20citizens%20and%20exacerbate%20case%20backlogs%20in%20an%20already%20overburdened%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20key%20new%20provisions%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETimely%20Court%20Rulings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Courts%20are%20now%20required%20to%20issue%20rulings%20within%2045%20days%20of%20the%20completion%20of%20arguments.%20Previously%2C%20no%20such%20time%20frame%20existed%2C%20often%20leading%20to%20prolonged%20cases.%20Additionally%2C%20charges%20in%20a%20trial%20must%20be%20framed%20within%2060%20days%20of%20the%20first%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExpedited%20Investigations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Police%20investigations%20into%20offences%20against%20women%20and%20children%20must%20be%20completed%20within%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESevere%20Punishments%20For%20Heinous%20Crimes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20death%20penalty%20has%20been%20prescribed%20for%20severe%20offences%20such%20as%20the%20gang-rape%20of%20a%20woman%20under%2018%20and%20mob%20lynching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevised%20Sedition%20Clauses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20government%20claims%20to%20have%20abolished%20sedition%20clauses%2C%20but%20a%20new%20clause%20punishing%20%26quot%3Bacts%20endangering%20the%20sovereignty%2C%20unity%2C%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20introduced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrials%20In%20Absentia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20For%20grave%20offences%2C%20trials%20in%20absentia%20are%20now%20permitted%20when%20the%20police%20cannot%20locate%20the%20accused.%20Judges%20can%20rule%20on%20such%20cases%2C%20and%20punishments%20will%20be%20enforced%20once%20the%20individual%20is%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMandatory%20Videotaping%20Of%20Police%20Actions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Police%20raids%20and%20seizures%20must%20be%20videotaped%2C%20and%20forensic%20experts%20are%20required%20to%20visit%20crime%20scenes%20for%20serious%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDigital%20Evidence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Digital%20records%20such%20as%20emails%2C%20server%20logs%2C%20messages%2C%20location%20data%2C%20and%20voicemails%20are%20now%20recognised%20as%20evidence%20during%20trials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommunity%20Service%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Community%20service%20is%20introduced%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20jail%20for%20offences%20like%20defamation%20and%20other%20petty%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20spearheaded%20the%20new%20laws%2C%20stated%20that%20the%20primary%20objective%20is%20to%20deliver%20justice%20rather%20than%20focus%20solely%20on%20penal%20actions%2C%20unlike%20the%20colonial-era%20laws.%20%26quot%3BThese%20laws%20are%20made%20by%20Indians%2C%20for%20Indians%2C%20and%20by%20an%20Indian%20Parliament%2C%20marking%20the%20end%20of%20colonial%20criminal%20justice%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20new%20legislation%20is%20not%20merely%20a%20change%20in%20nomenclature%20but%20a%20comprehensive%20overhaul.%20%26quot%3BThe%20soul%2C%20body%2C%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20new%20laws%20are%20Indian%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20remarked.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720438680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F8hulrkec_jail-generic_625x300_21_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-what-are-the-key-provisions-in-indias-new-criminal-laws-6060287%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20new%20criminal%20laws%20came%20into%20effect%20last%20month%2C%20bringing%20changes%20to%20India's%20criminal%20justice%20