l%20To%20Son%20After%20BMW%20Crash%2C%20A%20Big%20Porsche%20Case%20Parallel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20leader%20Rajesh%20Shah%20had%20asked%20his%20son%20Mihir%20to%20switch%20places%20with%20their%20driver%20Rajrishi%20Bidawat%20after%20the%20BMW%20car%20he%20was%20driving%20crashed%20into%20a%20scooter%20and%20dragged%20a%20woman%2C%20police%20told%20a%20Mumbai%20court%20today.%20The%20woman%2C%20Kaveri%20Nakhawa%2C%20died%20in%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20main%20accused%20Mihir%20Shah%20is%20on%20the%20run%2C%20his%20father%20Rajesh%20Shah%2C%20deputy%20leader%20of%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Sena%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Palghar%20district%2C%20and%20the%20family's%20driver%20Rajrishi%20Bidawat%20have%20been%20arrested.%20Police%20sources%20said%20they%20were%20not%20cooperating%20in%20the%20probe.%20They%20were%20produced%20in%20court%20today.%20Rajesh%20Shah%20was%20remanded%20in%20judicial%20custody%20till%20July%2013%20and%20the%20driver%20Bidawat%20in%20police%20custody%20for%20a%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMihir%20Shah%2C%20the%20police%20said%2C%20and%20his%20father%20Rajesh%20Shah%20made%20several%20calls%20to%20each%20other%20after%20the%20accident%20in%20Worli%20early%20yesterday%2C%20police%20have%20said.%20The%20Sena%20leader%2C%20they%20said%2C%20told%20his%20son%20to%20switch%20places%20with%20the%20driver%20and%20move%20to%20the%20seat%20next%20to%20the%20driver.%20The%20plan%2C%20police%20said%2C%20was%20to%20pin%20the%20blame%20for%20the%20crash%20on%20the%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20strikingly%20similar%20to%20what%20had%20transpired%20in%20the%20Porsche%20crash%20in%20Pune%20this%20February.%20After%20a%20late-night%20dash%20by%20a%2017-year-old%20son%20of%20a%20Pune%20realtor%20in%20his%20high-end%20car%20left%20two%2024-year-old%20engineers%20dead%2C%20the%20family%20had%20tried%20to%20make%20the%20driver%20take%20the%20blame.%20The%20driver%20had%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20confined%20and