0security%20at%20the%20event%20--%20a%20thanskgiving%20event%20organised%20by%20supporters%20of%20Karnataka%20BJP%20MP%20and%20former%20minister%20K%20Sudhakar%20has%20drawn%20criticism%20for%20free%20and%20public%20distribution%20of%20liquor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chikkballapur%20MP's%20supporters%20organised%20the%20event%20to%20thank%20people%20for%20his%20victory%20in%20the%20recently-held%20general%20election.%20BJP's%20K%20Sudhakar%20defeated%20Congress%20MS%20Raksha%20Ramaiah%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20more%20than%201.6%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20DK%20Shivakumar%20said%20BJP%20national%20president%20JP%20Nadda%20must%20issue%20a%20clarification.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20the%20local%20leaders%20to...%20I%20want%20the%20BJP%20national%20president%20to%20issue%20a%20clarification%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20the%20culture%20of%20the%20BJP%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20state%20government%20will%20take%20steps%20in%20this%20matter%20under%20the%20state%20excise%20policy%2C%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20the%20next%20point.%20First%2C%20let%20the%20party%20answer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20row%2C%20Mr%20Sudhakar%20said%20he%20is%20not%20aware%20if%20liquor%20was%20distributed%20by%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20event%20or%20those%20attending%20it%20brought%20their%20drinks%20along.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20had%20no%20connection%20to%20this.%20%26quot%3BIf%20this%20was%20done%20by%20workers%20of%20our%20party%20or%20the%20JDS%2C%20it's%20wrong.%20In%20my%2025%20years%20in%20politics%2C%20I%20have%20never%20distributed%20alcohol%20during%20elections%20or%20at%20any%20event.%20I%20have%20no%20connection%20to%20this%20issue.%20This%20has%20brought%20me%20pain%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20future%20too%2C%20be%20it%20any%20event%20or%20election%20campaign%2C%20alcohol%20must%20not%20be%20served.%20Serving%20alcohol%20like%20this%20is%20an%20offence%20and%20a%20blunder.%20I%20have%20spoken%20to%20them%20(organisers)%20over%20the%20phone%20last%20night.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20from%20the%20event%20show%20long%20queues%20and%20rush%20among%20people%20to%20collect%20liquor%20bottles.%20What's%20bizarre%20is%20that%20Mr%20Sudhakar%20had%20written%20to%20the%20local%20police%20ahead%20of%20the%20event%2C%20seeking%20police%20deployment%20for%20the%20event.%20And%20this%20letter%20mentioned%20that%20food%20and%20liquor%20will%20be%20served%20at%20the%20event.%20A%20big%20question%20then%20is%20why%20the%20event%20was%20allowed%20and%20cops%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20row%20over%20liquor%20distribution%2C%20CN%20Ashwath%20Narayan%2C%20former%20minister%20and%20BJP%20MLA%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20blame%20anybody%20unless%20this%20is%20properly%20looked%20into.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20system%2C%20the%20government%20would%20have%20fixed%20responsibility.%20If%20the%20government%20feels%20whatever%20has%20happened%20(is%20wrong)%2C%20let%20them%20take%20action.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720438380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fcek06iqg_karnataka-free-liquor_625x300_08_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fk-sudhakar-free-liquor-at-bjp-mps-post-poll-event-sparks-political-row-in-karnataka-6059442%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Crate%20after%20crate%20of%20liquor%20bottles%2C%20long%20queues%20of%20men%20waiting%20for%20their%20turn%20and%20police%20providing%20security%20at%20the%20event%20--%20a%20thanskgiving%20event%20organised%20by%20supporters%20of%20Karnataka%20BJP%20MP%20K%20Sudhakar%20has%20drawn%20criticism%20for%20free%20liquor%20distribution%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fk-s