%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20fuselage%20plug%20area%20of%20Alaska%20Airlines%20Flight%201282.%3Cp%3ENTSB%20via%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBoeing%20agreed%20to%20plead%20guilty%20to%20one%20count%20of%20fraud%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIts%20government%20contracts%2C%20worth%2037%25%20of%20last%20year's%20revenue%2C%20could%20be%20in%20jeopardy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPlus%20Boeing%20faces%20other%20investigations%20and%20lawsuits%20from%20Alaska%20Airlines%20passengers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-big-mea-culpa-just-dropped-does-not-look-pretty-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoeing%20has%20agreed%20to%20plead%20guilty%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20one%20count%20of%20fraud%20conspiracy%2C%20the%20Justice%20Department%20said%20in%20a%20Sunday%20court%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DoJ%20said%20Boeing%20violated%20a%202021%20deferred%20prosecution%20agreement.%20This%20deal%20was%20reached%20after%20346%20people%20died%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-crashes-groundings-timeline-737-max-777-air-force-tanker-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20737%20Max%20crashes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202018%20and%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-fine-settlement-charges-defraud-faa-737-max-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoeing%20had%20to%20pay%20%242.5%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20to%20the%20victims'%20families%20%E2%80%94%20and%20agreed%20to%20strengthen%20its%20compliance%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DPA%20was%20due%20to%20expire%20just%20two%20days%20after%20January's%20Alaska%20Airlines%20blowout.%20In%20May%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-subject-to-prosecution-over-737-max-crashes-doj-says-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJustice%20Department%20said%20Boeing%3C%2Fa%3E%20failed%20to%20%26quot%3Bdesign%2C%20implement%2C%20and%20enforce%20a%20compliance%20and%20ethics%20program.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESunday's%20plea%20deal%20will%20see%20Boeing%20pay%20an%20additional%20%24243.6%20million%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20criminal%20penalty%20as%20in%202021.%20Plus%2C%20it%20has%20been%20ordered%20to%20invest%20at%20least%20%24455%20million%20in%20its%20compliance%20and%20safety%20program%20and%20impose%20an%20independent%20monitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20will%20determine%20the%20restitution%20to%20be%20paid%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%202018%20and%202019%20crash%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20the%20end%20of%20the%20fallout%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Cassell%2C%20an%20attorney%20for%20the%20families%20of%20victims%20of%20the%202018%20and%202019%20crashes%2C%20slammed%20Sunday's%20plea%20deal%20and%20called%20on%20the%20judge%20to%20reject%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20sweetheart%20deal%20fails%20to%20recognize%20that%20because%20of%20Boeing's%20conspiracy%2C%20346%20people%20died%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BA%20judge%20can%20reject%20a%20plea%20deal%20that%20is%20not%20in%20the%20public%20interest%2C%20and%20this%20deceptive%20and%20generous%20deal%20is%20clearly%20not%20in%20the%20public%20interest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d8ff25ec-2a1f-45a5-9643-69fd98bd37be%5C%22%3EGovernment%20contracts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20pleading%20guilty%20to%20fraud%20conspiracy%2C%20Boeing%20will%20have%20committed%20a%20felony%20%E2%80%94%20jeopardizing%20its%20government%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20company's%20last%20annual%20report%2C%2037%25%20of%20its%20revenue%20came%20from%20government%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20primarily%20in%20the%20defense%20and%20space%20sectors%2C%20which%20have%20been%20a%20saving%20grace%20for%20Boeing%20as%20its%20commercial%20airplanes%20division%20suffered%20from%20January's%20blowout.%20Without%20them%2C%20Boeing's%20stock%20price%20would%20likely%20have%20fallen%20even%20further%20than%20the%2026%25%20it%20has%20dropped%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20each%20government%20agency%20has%20been%20left%20to%20decide%20whether%20to%20continue%20business%20with%20Boeing.%20As%20such%20a%20valued%20firm%2C%20it%20seems%20unlikely%20to%20suffer%20much%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Senate%20hearing%20about%20Boeing's%20safety%20culture%2C%20Richard%20Blumenthal%2C%20chair%20of%20the%20subcommittee%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BBoeing%20needs%20to%20succeed%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20jobs%20it%20provides%2C%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20local%20economies%20it%20supports%2C%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20American%20traveling%20public%2C%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20our%20military.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20there%20are%20other%20investigations%20that%20Boeing%20is%20facing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoj-opens-criminal-investigation-alaska-airlines-blowout-report-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJustice%20Department%20opened%20an%20investigation%20into%20Boeing%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20the%20Alaska%20Airlines%20blowout%2C%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20review%20of%20the%20DPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20month%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-tells-boeing-737-blowout-passengers-may-be-victims-crime-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFBI%20wrote%20to%20passengers%20on%20Alaska%20Airlines%20Flight%201282%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20identified%20you%20as%20a%20possible%20victim%20of%20a%20crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENumerous%20passengers%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falaska-airlines-passengers-hit-by-debris-faulty-oxygen-masks-lawsuit-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esu