2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Reformist%20In%20Iran%2C%20'Changemaker'%20In%20UK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDifferent%20nations%2C%20different%20challenges%2C%20different%20political%20arcs%2C%20but%20all%20facing%20a%20moment%20of%20political%20reckoning.%20Ironically%2C%20it%20is%20Iran%20where%20the%20recent%20change%20of%20leadership%20holds%20the%20most%20promise.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20a%20reformist%20has%20come%20to%20power%20in%20Iran%20in%20a%20system%20that%20has%20been%20dominated%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Bsupreme%20leader%26quot%3B%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20since%201989.%20The%20conservatives%20have%20controlled%20all%20the%20levers%20of%20power%20and%20have%20managed%20to%20scuttle%20earlier%20reformists%20like%20Mohammad%20Khatami%20and%20Hassan%20Rouhani.%20However%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20growing%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20ruling%20elites.%20By%20criticising%20Iran's%20morality%20police%20and%20promising%20%26quot%3Bunity%20and%20cohesion%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0as%20well%20as%20an%20end%20to%20Iran's%20%26quot%3Bisolation%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20world%2C%20Pezeshkian%20talked%20in%20a%20language%20that%20appealed%20to%20those%20who%20want%20normalcy%20in%20a%20nation%20that%20has%20been%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20precipice%20for%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishi%20Sunak%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20not%20only%20bogged%20down%20by%20the%20legacy%20of%20his%20predecessors%20who%20had%20made%20a%20mockery%20of%20public%20mandates%2C%20but%20he%20was%20also%20unable%20to%20soothe%20the%20British%20public%20struggling%20with%20rising%20costs%20of%20living%20and%20a%20crumbling%20public%20services%20infrastructure.%20The%20Conservative%20Party%20imploded%2C%20and%20Sunak's%20leadership%20never%20managed%20to%20rise%20to%20match%20the%20needs%20of%20today's%20Britain.%20And%20so%2C%20the%20Labour%20Party%20ended%20up%20getting%20a%20landslide%20even%20without%20increasing%20its%20vote%20share%2C%20thereby%20taking%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20in%20a%20direction%20opposite%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20Europe%2C%20where%20the%20Right%20is%20ascending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EClose%20Shave%20For%20Macron%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20France%2C%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20had%20to%20call%20a%20snap%20election%20fearing%20the%20resurgence%20of%20the%20nation's%20far-right%20party%2C%20the%20National%20Rally%20(RN).%20Only%20a%20last-minute%2C%20left-wing%20tactical%20adjustment%20could%20prevent%20an%20outright%20landslide%20for%20the%20RN.%20But%20this%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20just%20a%20consolation%20prize%2C%20as%20the%20RN%20has%20greatly%20increased%20its%20representation%20in%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrance-legislative-elections-disaster-averted-emmanuel-macron-still-faces-big-challenge-ahead-6056303%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0Disaster%20Averted%2C%20But%20Macron%20Still%20Faces%20Big%20Challenge%20Ahead%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20last%20month%2C%20the%20European%20Union%20elections%20saw%20a%20resurgence%20of%20the%20right%20in%20ways%20few%20had%20anticipated%2C%20and%20the%20triumph%20of%20Eurosceptic%20parties%20will%20have%20serious%20long-term%20consequences%20for%20the%20ability%20of%20the%2027-member%20bloc%20to%20work%20cohesively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EConcerns%20About%20Biden%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20eyes%2C%20however%2C%20are%20now%20on%20the%20leadership%20contest%20in%20the%20US%2C%20where%20two%20old%20white%20men%20are%20busy%20damaging%20the%20brand%20of%20American%20democracy.%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20under%20whose%20presidency%20the%20foundations%20of%20the%20American%20democratic%20institutional%20fabric%20came%20close%20to%20collapsing%2C%20continues%20to%20be%20ahead%20in%20the%20presidential%20race%2C%20as%20the%20base%20of%20the%20Republican%20Party%20c