h%20her%20fingers.%20%26quot%3BThey%20collect%20the%20extra%20blood%20and%20other%20fluids%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20accumulating%20in%20my%20body.%20I%20have%20to%20dump%20the%20contents%20a%20couple%20times%20a%20day%20and%20keep%20track%20of%20how%20much%20comes%20out%20to%20make%20sure%20it's%20less%20each%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20showed%20me%20a%20little%20notebook%20with%20a%20list%20of%20dates%20and%20measurements%20in%20decreasing%20amounts.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20little%20gross%2C%20but%20they're%20only%20there%20for%20a%20few%20more%20days%2C%20until%20they%20stop%20filling%20up%20with%20gunk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20like%20a%20%3Cem%3Elot%20%3C%2Fem%3Egross%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20said%2C%20recoiling%20slightly%2C%20which%20got%20a%20laugh%20out%20of%20Stephanie.%20I'd%20been%20peed%20on%20by%20my%20kids%20and%20caught%20their%20vomit%20in%20my%20bare%20hands%20without%20batting%20an%20eye%2C%20but%20medical%20gore%20made%20my%20insides%20churn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreast-cancer-survivors-racing-to-get-surgery-before-insurance-change-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoptions%20for%20reconstruction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she'd%20chosen%20silicone%20implants%20with%20an%20overlay%20of%20muscle%20taken%20from%20her%20upper%20back%20to%20give%20her%20%26quot%3Bfoobs%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20fake%20boobs%20%E2%80%94%20a%20more%20natural%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I%20have%20to%20do%20is%20sit%20on%20my%20couch%20propped%20up%20with%20these%20pillows%2C%20some%20physical%20therapy%20to%20regain%20range%20of%20motion%20in%20my%20arms%2C%20and%20I'll%20be%20good%20as%20new%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20reassured%20me.%20%26quot%3BBetter%2C%20even.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228fc5ebba-1e02-46f5-85a6-877a2efb3301%5C%22%3EI%20asked%20for%20the%20BRCA%20test%2C%20and%20my%20doctor%20agreed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20next%20prenatal%20checkup%2C%20I%20asked%20my%20doctor%20to%20arrange%20a%20BRCA%20test.%20The%20OB-GYN%20practice%20had%20started%20to%20see%20an%20uptick%20in%20requests%20for%20this%20type%20of%20blood%20test.%20She%20agreed%20that%20for%20me%2C%20it%20was%20a%20no-brainer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20make%20sure%20to%20have%20the%20test%20kit%20here%20for%20your%20next%20check-up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20are%20you%20sure%20you%20want%20to%20do%20this%20while%20you're%20pregnant%3F%26quot%3B%20She%20was%20concerned%20about%20the%20psychological%20toll%20of%20potentially%20finding%20out%20I%20was%20a%20carrier%20at%20a%20time%20when%20I%20was%20already%20hormonal%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20doctor%20was%20cautious%20but%20never%20alarmist.%20It%20was%20hard%20to%20say%20how%20old%20she%20was.%20Her%20wiry%20gray%20hair%20was%20always%20pulled%20back%20into%20a%20messy%20ponytail%2C%20and%20she%20favored%20socks%20with%20Birkenstocks%20and%20rimless%20glasses%2C%20which%20probably%20added%20years%20to%20her%20actual%20age.%20What%20mattered%20to%20me%20was%20that%20she'd%20been%20in%20the%20expectant-mother%20game%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbsolutely%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20said%20without%20reservation.%20Whatever%20the%20test%20results%2C%20I%20was%20already%20plotting%20my%20next%20preventive%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHave%20you%20decided%20what%20to%20do%20if%20it%20turns%20out%20you're%20BRCA%20positive%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked%2C%20wheeling%20her%20little%20stool%20over%20to%20her%20desk%20to%20make%20some%20notes%20in%20my%20chart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEither%20way%2C%20I'm%20getting%20rid%20of%20these%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20announced%2C%20grabbing%20a%20swollen%20breast%20in%20each%20hand.%20%26quot%3BNo%20question.%20I%20don't%20want%20this%20threat%20looming%20over%20me%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EExcerpted%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheexperimentpublishing.com%2Fcatalo