d%20to%20brutal%20torture%20for%2022%20days%20before%20being%20killed.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20an%20interview%2C%20Captain%20Kalia's%20parents%2C%20Dr%20Narendra%20Kalia%20and%20Mrs%20Vijaya%20Kalia%2C%20recalled%20the%20pain%20and%20devastation%20they%20felt%20upon%20learning%20of%20their%20son's%20death.%20However%2C%20the%20outpouring%20of%20love%20and%20respect%20from%20people%20across%20the%20country%20has%20given%20them%20some%20comfort%2C%20they%20say.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWho%20was%20Captain%20Saurabh%20Kalia%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnCaptain%20Saurabh%20Kalia%20was%20born%20on%20January%2029%2C%201976%2C%20in%20Amritsar%2C%20and%20grew%20up%20in%20Palampur%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20He%20completed%20his%20schooling%20at%20DAV%20Public%20School%20and%20higher%20secondary%20education%20at%20Kendriya%20Vidyalaya%20in%20Palampur.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDriven%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20serve%20the%20country%2C%20Saurabh%20Kalia%20joined%20the%20army%20through%20the%20CDSR%20and%20was%20commissioned%20as%20an%20officer%20in%204%20Jat%20on%20December%2012%2C%201998.%20He%20was%20deployed%20to%20Kargil%2C%20where%20he%20managed%20general%20duties%20at%20the%20Baharng%20Complex%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%20over%2017%2C000%20feet%20and%20monitored%20infiltrations%20in%20the%20Kaksar%20sub-sector.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%20to%20Captain%20Saurabh%20Kalia%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20May%2015%2C%201999%2C%20Captain%20Kalia%20and%20five%20soldiers%20were%20on%20a%20routine%20patrol%20when%20they%20were%20ambushed%20and%20captured%20alive%20by%20Pakistani%20forces.%20They%20were%20held%20captive%20for%2022%20days%20and%20tortured%20to%20death.%20Their%20bodies%20were%20returned%20by%20the%20Pakistani%20army%20on%20June%209%2C%201999.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnCaptain%20Saurabh%20Kalia's%20mother%20recalls%20learning%20of%20her%20son's%20death%20through%20a%20newspaper%20article%2C%20a%20pain%20that%20lingers%2025%20years%20later.%20They%20went%20to%20confirm%20the%20news%20at%20the%20Palampur%20army%20office%20and%20were%20met%20with%20the%20stark%20reality%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20news%20is%20good%20news%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20military.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThough%20time%20has%20somewhat%20eased%20her%20grief%2C%20the%20inhumane%20torture%20inflicted%20on%20Saurabh%20and%20his%20comrades%20continues%20to%20haunt%20her.%20Captain%20Saurabh%20Kalia's%20father%20remembers%20his%20son%20as%20a%20calm%20and%20thoughtful%20person.%20He%20has%20been%20fighting%20for%20justice%20for%20his%20son's%20mistreatment%2C%20but%20the%20government%20has%20not%20taken%20action%20as%20of%20yet.%20He%20even%20took%20the%20case%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20progress%20since%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20the%2025th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Kargil%20War%2C%20Captain%20Kargil's%20father%20appealed%20to%20all%20citizens%20to%20show%20respect%20and%20gratitude%20to%20soldiers%20who%20served%20the%20nation%20in%20extreme%20conditions%2C%20from%20-50%20to%20%2B50%20degrees%20Celsius.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20Pakistan%20can't%20be%20trusted%2C%20like%20a%20dog's%20tail%20that%20will%20never%20straighten.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EKargil%20War%C2%A0(1999)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndia%20and%20Pakistan%20were%20involved%20in%20a%20war%20from%20May%20to%20July%201999%20in%20the%20Kargil%20district%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20conflict%20began%20when%20Pakistani%20troops%20infiltrated%20Indian%20positions%20across%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC).%20In%20response%2C%20India%20launched%20Operations%20Vijay%20and%20Safed%20Sagar%20to%20reclaim%20the%20occupied%20territories.%20The%20war%20included%20significant%20battles%2C%20such%20as%20the%20recapture%20of%20Tiger%20Hill%20and%20Tololing.%20Ultimately%2C%20India%20won%2C%20forcing%20Pakistan%20to%20withdraw%20its%20troops.%20The%20conflict%20ended%20with%20a%20return%20to%20the%20pre-conflict%20status%20quo.%20India%20suffered%20527%20casualties%20during%20the%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720430760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Fo8krtkfo_capt-saurabh-kaliakargil-war-hero-_625x300_21_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkargil-war-heros-parents-recall-pain-of-martyrdom-25-years-on-6058963%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Twenty-five%20years%20ago%2C%20Captain%20Saurabh%20Kalia%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20army%20officer%20to%20be%20killed%20in%20the%20Kargil%20War.%20He%20was%20captured%20by%20Pakistani%20forces%20along%20with%20five%20other%20soldiers%20and%20subjected%20to%20brutal%20torture%20for%2022%20days%20before%20being%20killed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkargil-war-heros-parents-recall-pain-of-martyrdom-25-years-on-6058963%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkargil-war-heros-parents-recall-pain-of-martyrdom-25-years-on-6058963%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkargil-war-heros-parents-recall-pain-of-martyrdom-25-years-on-6058963%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDon't%20Leave%20Home%20If%20Not%20Needed%26quot%3B%3A%20E%20Shinde's%20Appeal%20After%20Rain%20Halts%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20heavy%20overnight%20rain%20left%20Mumbai%20struggling%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20on%20Monday%20appealed%20to%20people%20not%20to%20leave%20home%20unless%20necessary.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20also%20asked%20the%20Police%20Commissioner%20not%20to%20allow%20anyone%20near%20the%20beaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20areas%20in%20Mumbai%20received%20300%20mm%20of%20rainfall%20between%201-7%20am%20this%20morning%2C%20leaving%20the%20streets%20wat