an%20from%20Singapore%20on%20a%20merchant%20vessel%20with%2020%20men.%20As%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20she%20received%20a%20cold%20welcome%20even%20before%20she%20could%20place%20her%20suitcase%20in%20her%20cabin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20manager%20had%20never%20seen%20a%20woman%20in%20this%20role.%20He%20was%20really%20dominating%20and%20kept%20telling%20me%20that%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20do%20this%20job.%20It%20was%20extremely%20demotivating.%20Imagine%20listening%20to%20this%20all%20the%20time!%20I%20survived%20the%20four%20months%20and%20proved%20him%20wrong%20through%20my%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20ETO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20proudly%20shares%20that%20at%20the%20end%20of%20her%20first%20contract%2C%20the%20same%20manager%20who%20had%20initially%20judged%20her%20conducted%20her%20appraisal.%20He%20gave%20her%20a%20good%20recommendation%20and%20told%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20wrong%20to%20judge%20you%20without%20seeing%20your%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20interviewed%20Romeeta%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20ponder%20how%20water%20has%20no%20ceiling%2C%20but%20even%20there%2C%20men%20have%20built%20a%20glass%20ceiling%2C%20which%20she%20successfully%20broke.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20gave%20you%20the%20strength%20and%20fortitude%20to%20face%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20ask.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20colleagues%20were%20nice%20to%20me%20to%20my%20face%20but%20they%20all%20thought%20that%20I%20was%20not%20capable%20just%20because%20of%20my%20gender.%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20this%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fwp-admin%2Fadmin.php%3Fpage%3Dstats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproblem%20faced%20by%20women%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20land%20jobs%20too%3F%20All%20you%20can%20do%20is%20focus%20and%20work%20hard%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20replies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20keeping%20her%20chin%20up%20and%20focusing%20on%20excelling%20at%20her%20job%2C%20she%20silenced%20all%20her%20