ys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20then%2C%20my%20classmates%20had%20already%20picked%20their%20topics%20ranging%20from%20plastic%20and%20sanitary%20napkins%20to%20thermocol.%20I%20was%20hardly%20left%20with%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20clueless%20Radhesh%20was%20asked%20to%20leave%20the%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpset%20with%20this%2C%20he%20craved%20a%20chicken%20dish%20to%20uplift%20his%20mood%20and%20went%20to%20the%20butcher%E2%80%99s%20to%20purchase%20some.%20%E2%80%9CI%20asked%20him%20to%20pack%201%20kg%20of%20chicken%20but%20the%20packet%20weighed%20only%20650%20gram%2C%20while%20he%20charged%20me%20for%20a%20kilo.%20He%20said%20the%20remaining%20350%20gram%20was%20waste.%20I%20then%20asked%20him%20to%20pack%20that%20separately%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20he%20took%20this%20very%20bag%20to%20his%20college%2C%20leaving%20the%20class%20disgusted.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20opened%20the%20bag%2C%20some%20people%20puked%20as%20it%20stunk.%20I%20was%20thrown%20out%20of%20the%20class%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-1-1718797523.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Radhesh%20runs%20%E2%80%98Golden%20Feathers%E2%80%99%20which%20upcycles%20chicken%20butchery%20waste%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98wool-like%E2%80%99%20fibre.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-1-1718797523.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-1-1718797523-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-1-1718797523-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%