dhesh%20remarks%20that%20in%20a%20country%20where%20rivers%20are%20worshipped%20as%20mothers%2C%20the%20butchery%20waste%20comprising%20intestines%2C%20blood%2C%20skin%2C%20inner%20cells%2C%20and%20feathers%2C%20ends%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F297496%2Framon-magsaysay-award-winner-gary-bencheghib-cleans-plastic-from-bali-indonesia-beaches%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolluting%20river%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20also%20spreads%20communicable%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWaste%20from%20big%20bovine%20animals%20is%20used%20to%20make%20leather%2C%20pet%20foods%2C%20and%20more%2C%20whereas%20chicken%20butchery%20waste%20is%20either%20incinerated%20or%20ends%20up%20in%20landfills%20and%20water%20bodies.%20The%20incineration%20process%20releases%20huge%20amounts%20of%20carbon%20emissions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20the%20entire%20world%20is%20working%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F319912%2Ftamil-nadu-father-son-duo-senthil-kumar-recycle-plastic-bottles-into-sustainable-clothes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20recycling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20not%20many%20are%20talking%20about%20chicken%20butchery%20waste.%20However%2C%20instead%20of%20making%20slogans%20to%20clean%20water%20bodies%2C%20we%20really%20need%20to%20work%20on%20grassroots%20to%20solve%20the%20root%20causes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20shawls%2C%20quilts%2C%20and%20paper%20from%20chicken%20waste%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20do%20his%20bit%2C%20Radhesh%20launched%20his%20company%20in%202019.%20Explaining%20its%20functioning%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20we%20collect%20waste%20from%20slaughterhouses%20and%20then%20we%20sterilise%20and%20sanitise%20it%20in%20a%20hygienic%20way%20using%20100%20degr