%20painful.%20I%20could%20hardly%20go%20out%20of%20the%20room%20before%20wanting%20to%20give%20up%20and%20get%20back%20to%20bed.%20But%20my%20dad%20made%20a%20rule%20that%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20felt%20like%20giving%20up%2C%20I%20would%20take%20five%20more%20steps%20and%20then%20make%20a%20U-turn%20back%20to%20the%20room.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20small%20motivations%20made%20Sakshi%E2%80%99s%20recovery%20easier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWatching%20Sakshi%E2%80%99s%20journey%20unravel%20has%20been%20all-inspiring%20to%20many%2C%20particularly%20her%20sister%20Isha%2C%20who%20looks%20up%20to%20her%20as%20a%20role%20model.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20many%20younger%20siblings%20get%20the%20opportunity%20to%20see%20their%20elder%20siblings%20grow%20up%20in%20front%20of%20them.%20I%20salute%20her%20willpower%20and%20I%20often%20tell%20her%20that%20she%20is%20the%20main%20character%20of%20my%20life!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsha%20smiles%20as%20she%20remembers%20the%20day%20her%20%3Cem%3Edidi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(elder%20sister)%20got%20admission%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F170564%2Fahmedabad-uttarayan-rescue-crane-doc-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorthopaedics%20%3C%2Fa%3Edepartment%20at%20the%20BJ%20Medical%20College%2C%20Ahmedabad.%20%E2%80%9CI%20baked%20a%20cake%20and%20we%20celebrated%20it%20like%20a%20festival!%E2%80%9D%20she%20exclaims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdversity%20had%20taught%20the%20family%20to%20cherish%20the%20small%20wins.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20the%20first%20time%20after%20the%20accident%20when%20my%20sister%20was%20able%20to%20open%20the%20cap%20on%20the%20toothpaste%20tube%20and%20brush%20her%20teeth%20by%20herself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Isha%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20memory%20that%20eclipses%20all%20others%20for%20Isha%20is%20the%20day%20Sakshi%20took%20her%20first%20steps%20without%20support.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20us%2